Zinc Binding Sites
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Zinc(II) binding proteins are extremely diverse in structure and function.
 Zn(II) is a intermediate Lewis acid in terms of hardness according to the
 
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
gls{hsab}
\end_layout

\end_inset

